{"tid":330941,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返左個令月intern，啱啱聽返農夫d歌有少少想喊","createTime":"2017-07-21T16:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T12:49:03.000Z","uid":1249,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"241dc7ec3e10cafe532812672a4266dfd9cff314","tid":330941,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:38:19.000Z","msg":"啱啱ot完返到屋企，原來依家聽農夫d歌感覺經已唔同晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n粒粒皆辛苦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oGPoBvtXRAY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoGPoBvtXRAY&d=CKgDxfPOCJFUynQvfp2Tj%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ca017403\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oGPoBvtXRAY</a><br />\n聽朝又八點九 一步一步走嘅一個一個年頭<br />\n為咗走去盡頭 一粒一粒都係辛苦嘅嗰日終於接受<br />\n終於 知道 粒粒皆辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你的志願<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=itP4J3Bx9Wk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DitP4J3Bx9Wk&d=CKgDxfPOCJFUynQvfp2Tj%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=be4fb6eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=itP4J3Bx9Wk</a><br />\n幾耐之前 你依然<br />\n仲有夢想 去實現<br />\n一年又一年 你的志願<br />\n已經唔再係你的自傳<br />\n逐漸 變成你父母嘅續篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重新找到你<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WNzwm-Sv3PA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWNzwm-Sv3PA&d=CKgDxfPOCJFUynQvfp2Tj%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=04fb16e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WNzwm-Sv3PA</a><br />\n早半生已充滿遺憾天天仿佛影印<br />\n如今過了大半生 <br />\n原來從來你也不甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2729be62575d8bba26c434c06da95f54aae9bf84","tid":330941,"uid":15471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:40:59.000Z","msg":"諗住幾時跳樓？"},{"pid":"56d4a65a